                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Written in a very fine handwriting.</seg>
                        <date notBefore="1400" notAfter="1499">15th century</date>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red</seg>
                        <desc>
                           Old palaeographical features: 
                           ዐ and sometimes መ and ሠ have angular shapes; 
                           the upper part of ቆ, ቶ, የ, ደ, and ጸ have an angular shape;
                           ሎ has the loop marking the 7th order attached directly to the body of the letter, without the linking line (it is written with the linking line on 
                           <locus target="#52r1"/>, cp. also <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/VAZ6GVMU"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:ContiRossini1896Vergine"/><title level="a">La redazione etiopica della preghiera della Vergine tra i Parti</title><title level="j">Atti della Reale Accademia dei Lincei, Rendiconti, Classe di scienze morale, storiche e filologiche</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Carlo</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Conti Rossini</t:surname></author><date>1896</date><biblScope unit="volume">Serie quinta, 5</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">457-479</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">461 n. 1</citedRange></bibl> 
                           and <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/MZC4PZ7D"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:ContiRossini1914Notice"/><title level="m">Notice sur les manuscrits éthiopiens de la Collection d’Abbadie</title><title level="s">Extrait du Journal Asiatique</title><author><forename>Carlo</forename><surname>Conti Rossini</surname></author><pubPlace>Paris</pubPlace><publisher>Imprimerie nationale</publisher><date>1914</date><series><title level="s">Extrait du Journal Asiatique</title></series><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">Bibliothèque Nationale</note><note type="tag">bm:ContiRossini1914Notice</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">Bibliothèque Nationale</note><note type="tag">bm:ContiRossini1914Notice</note><citedRange unit="page">14</citedRange></bibl>); 
                           the left stroke of በ and ዘ is slanted;  
                           አ is sometimes written in the fourth order in words like ኣነ፡, ኣመ፡ and እግዚኣብሔር፡ (cp. also <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/VAZ6GVMU"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:ContiRossini1896Vergine"/><title level="a">La redazione etiopica della preghiera della Vergine tra i Parti</title><title level="j">Atti della Reale Accademia dei Lincei, Rendiconti, Classe di scienze morale, storiche e filologiche</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Carlo</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Conti Rossini</t:surname></author><date>1896</date><biblScope unit="volume">Serie quinta, 5</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">457-479</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">461 n. 1</citedRange></bibl>).
                        </desc>
                        <seg type="rubrication">
                           Titles, initial lines on the incipit page of the text, lines written in form of spiral in the left margin for ornamental purposes.
                        </seg>
