                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1">
                        <locus target="#4v"/>
                        <desc>Our Lady Mary and the Child. Legend:
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                              
                                 <sic>ሠዕለ፡</sic>
                               እግዝእትነ፡ 
                        ማ<supplied reason="omitted">ር</supplied>ያም፡ ምስለ፡ ፍቁር፡ ወልዳ።</q>.</desc>
                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2">
                        <locus target="#55v"/>
                        <desc>Our Lady Mary praying with open hands. Legend:
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ሥዕለ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘከ<supplied reason="omitted">መ፡</supplied> 
                           ትጼሊ፡ ቀዊማ፡ ጸሎታ፡ ይዕቀበነ።</q>.</desc>
                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3">
                        <locus target="#62v"/>
                        <desc>
                           <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7743Paul">St Paul</persName>. Legend:
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ሥዕለ፡ ቅዱስ፡ 
                                 <sic>ጰውሎስ፡</sic>
                              
                           </q>.
                        </desc>
                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d4">
                        <locus target="#110v"/>
                        <desc>
                           <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7953Prochoru">Prochorus</persName>. Legend:
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ሥዕለ፡ ቅዱስ፡ 
                           አብራ<supplied reason="explanation">ኮሮስ፡</supplied>
                           </q>.</desc>
                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <desc type="StampExlibris">Stamp</desc>
                           <locus target="#1r"/>
                           <note>Seal of the <ref type="ins" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0303BNF">Bibliothèque Nationale de France</ref>.</note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <desc type="ProtectivePrayer">Prayer to God</desc>
                           <locus target="#2r"/>
                           <note>The prayer terminates as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">እስመ፡ ዚአከ፡ ይእቲ፡ መንግሥት፡ ኀይል፡ ወስብሐት፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</q>.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <desc type="CalendaricNote">List of the commemorative feasts of the apostles</desc>
                           <locus target="#3r"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                              አመ፡ ፩ለመስከረም፡ በርተሎሜዎስ። አመ፡ ፲ወ፪ለጥቅምት፡ ማቴዎስ፨ አመ፡ ፲፰ለሕዳር፡ 
                                 <sic>ፊልጰስ፡</sic>
                               አመ፡ ፬፡ ለታኅሣሥ፡ እንድርያስ። አመ፡ ፬ለጥር፡ ዮሐንስ፨ 
                              አመ፡ ፲ለየካቲት፡ ያዕቆብ፡ አመ፡ ፰ለመጋቢት፡ ማትያስ፡ አመ፡ ፲፯፡ ለሚያዝያ፡ ያዕቆብ፡ ወዮሐንስ፡ አመ፡ ፳፮ለግንቦት፡ ቶማስ፨ አመ፡ ፪ለኀምሌ፡ ታዴዎስ፡ አመ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ 
                                 <sic>ወጰውሎስ፡</sic>
                               
                              አመ፡ ፲ናትናኤል፡ አመ፡ ያዕቆብ፡ አመ፡ ፲፰ቂርቆስ፨ = ፨ አመ፡ ፴ለነሐሴ፡ እንድርያስ፡
                           </q>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <desc type="GuestText">Untitled prayer to Our Lady Mary</desc>
                           <locus from="161r" to="164v"/>
                           <note> The prayer begins as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">አነ፡ ዕዝራ፡ ግዱፍ፡ ለማኅበረ፡ 
                                    <sic>በርያ፡</sic>
                                  ወንዋይየኒ፡ ግዱፍ፡ ወለዛቲ፡ ጸሎተ፡ 
                              ማርያም፡ ንዋዮሙ፡ ኢይንሥእዋ፡ ካልእ፡</q>. It terminates as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">ኦንጽሕት፡ 
                                    <sic>ኣንጽሕኒ፡</sic>
                                  በንጽኅኪ፡ ኦቅድስት፡ 
                                 ቀድስኒ፡ በቅድስ<supplied reason="omitted">ና</supplied>ኪ፡ <del rend="erasure" extent="two lines"/> 
                                 <choice>
                                    <sic>ኦቡርካት፡</sic>
                                    <corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ኦቡርክት፡</corr>
                                 </choice>
                                 
                                    <sic>በርኪኒ፡</sic>
                                  
                                 ወበረከትኪ፡ ወ<supplied reason="omitted">አ</supplied>ጽንዕኒ፡ በፍቅርኪ፡ ለዓለም።</q>.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                           <desc type="StampExlibris">Stamp</desc>
                           <locus target="#165r"/>
                           <note>Seal of the <ref type="ins" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0303BNF">Bibliothèque Nationale de France</ref>.</note>
                        </item>
                        
                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <locus target="#Iv"/>
                           <desc>The shelfmark of the Vatican Library <q>42</q> is written in a <date>18th-century</date> hand.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e2">
                           <locus target="#IIr"/>
                           <desc>The title of the book <q xml:lang="it">Historia della Madonna</q>was erroneously written by <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11238Contelori">Felice Contelori</persName>.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e3">
                           <locus target="#1"/>
                           <desc>Pen trial.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e4">
                           <desc>The name of the owner or of the scribe, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11379GabraHer">Gabra Ḫer</persName>, is written in the supplication 
                              formulas throughout the manuscript, e.g. on <locus target="#64r #67v #68v #76v #79v #83r #87v #88v #93r #99v #102v #104v #105r                                   #106r #109r #111r #118v #120r"/>. The names of other individuals are also written: <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11381Abranyos">ʾAbrānyos</persName> 
                              (<locus target="#92r"/>), <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11382Nob">Nob</persName> together with <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11379GabraHer">Gabra Ḫer</persName> 
                              (<locus target="#115v"/>).
                           </desc>
                        </item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
            
